track_notes: Park at the Col de Brouis, the path is a bit hard in the beginning. No problem on summit for antenna!
I used my VTT on the small military road, until the Blockhaus, then finished the last few meters by foot.

1 hour to climb the +450m you can park on the road near the starting plate saying Mont Gros 1h30mn
Plenty room for antenna, get some water in summertime
